<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1437,942,1983]" pageId="5" pageNumber="417">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,436,1922,1947]" pageId="5" pageNumber="417">Material examined.</emphasis>
<typeStatus box="[447,551,1923,1947]" pageId="5" pageNumber="417">Holotype</typeStatus>
(male) and eight 
<typeStatus box="[766,874,1924,1948]" pageId="5" pageNumber="417">paratypes</typeStatus>
(male and two females; sex not studied in five specimens): 
<collectingCountry box="[292,352,1959,1983]" name="India" pageId="5" pageNumber="417">India</collectingCountry>
, Tripura, Maharanipur, leaf debris underneath shrubs, collected by 0 5.04. 
<number box="[1174,1232,1959,1983]" pageId="5" pageNumber="417" value="1976.0">1976</number>
, S. Sarkar.
</paragraph>
<caption httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/218839/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="418" targetBox="[152,1433,216,1940]" targetPageId="6">
<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1436,1941,2024]" pageId="6" pageNumber="418">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,331,1941,1964]" pageId="6" pageNumber="418">FIGURES 11–15</emphasis>
. 
<taxonomicName box="[345,576,1941,1963]" class="Arachnida" family="Galumnidae" genus="Pergalumna" kingdom="Animalia" order="Sarcoptiformes" pageId="6" pageNumber="418" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mahunkai" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[345,576,1941,1963]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="418">Pergalumna mahunkai</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[582,663,1942,1963]" pageId="6" pageNumber="418" rank="species">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[582,663,1942,1963]" pageId="6" pageNumber="418">sp. nov.</emphasis>
</taxonomicNameLabel>
, adult: 11—dorsal view of body (right pteromorph not shown), 12—ventral view of body (anal plates and legs not shown), 13—dorso-lateral view of prodorsum, 14—posterior view of notogaster, 15— right pteromorpha. Scale bar 100 μm.
</paragraph>
